<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes">
    <title>三角洲行动 · 改枪码便签 | 公告版</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #f4f6f9; --card-bg: #ffffff; --text: #1e293b; --text-secondary: #64748b;
            --border: #e2e8f0; --accent: #1e3a5f; --accent-light: #eef2f6; --input-bg: #f8fafc;
